com.symantec.dlpx.flexresponse.discover

Interface GenericContentItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ContentItem, DiscoverItem, Locatable, RemediatedItem

    public interface GenericContentItem
extends DiscoverItem, Locatable
    The content item type for content that this crawled using the Web Services target. The Web Services target exposes a Web Service API for feeding arbitrary content to the Discover Server. The format of this content, therefore, is generic, since it may come from any number of content repository types.
